# ─── IMPORTANT: Clerk JWT Template Setup ─────────────────────────────────────
# You MUST create a JWT Template in Clerk for Convex auth to work:
#   1. Go to https://dashboard.clerk.com → your app
#   2. Configure → JWT Templates → New template
#   3. Name: "convex" (exact, lowercase)
#   4. Claims: {"aud": "convex"}
#   5. Save
#
# Then set the Clerk Frontend API URL as a Convex env var (NOT here):
#   npx convex env set CLERK_FRONTEND_API_URL https://your-app.clerk.accounts.dev
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
